    <section>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <div class="callout">
        For questions or concerns regarding these Terms, contact <strong>notcassal</strong> on Discord or join the support server: <a href="https://discord.gg/Gz3dEH9VpJ" target="_blank">discord.gg/Gz3dEH9VpJ</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <!-- PRIVACY POLICY -->
  <div class="page" id="privacy">
    <div class="page-header">
      <div class="eyebrow">XD Bot</div>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class="meta">Effective date: June 10, 2026 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Last updated: June 10, 2026</div>
    </div>

    <section>
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>XD Bot is a Discord bot developed and maintained by <strong>notcassal</strong>. This policy explains what data we collect, how it is used, and your rights regarding that data.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Data We Collect</h2>
      <p>When you interact with XD Bot, the following data is stored:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Discord User ID and username</li>
        <li>In-bot currency balance (Primogems)</li>
        <li>Gacha character collection</li>
        <li>Experience points (XP) and level</li>
        <li>Marriage status (Discord User ID of partner)</li>
        <li>Daily claim and vote timestamps</li>
        <li>Achievement progress</li>
        <li>AFK status and reason (temporary, in-memory only)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Server Data</h2>
      <p>For servers that use XD Bot's configuration features, we store:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Discord Guild (Server) ID</li>
        <li>Level-up announcement channel ID (if configured)</li>
        <li>Invite tracking channel ID (if configured)</li>
        <li>Invite usage records for invite tracking</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>How We Use Your Data</h2>
      <p>All collected data is used exclusively to operate the Bot's features. We do not:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Sell or share your data with third parties</li>
        <li>Use your data for advertising or marketing</li>
        <li>Store message content</li>
        <li>Track your activity outside of Bot interactions</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Data Storage</h2>
      <p>Data is stored securely on MongoDB Atlas. Access is restricted to the Bot's operator (notcassal). We take reasonable precautions to protect stored data but cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Data Retention & Deletion</h2>
      <p>Your data is retained for as long as you use the Bot. You may request deletion of your data at any time by contacting us. Upon a valid deletion request, all personally identifiable data associated with your Discord User ID will be removed within a reasonable timeframe.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>XD Bot interacts with the following external services:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Top.gg</strong> — for vote tracking (governed by Top.gg's own privacy policy)</li>
        <li><strong>nekos.best / otakugifs.xyz</strong> — for social action GIFs (no user data is sent)</li>
        <li><strong>meme-api.com</strong> — for meme content (no user data is sent)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Contact & Data Requests</h2>
      <div class="callout">
        To request data deletion or ask about your data, contact <strong>notcassal</strong> on Discord or join the support server: <a href="https://discord.gg/Gz3dEH9VpJ" target="_blank">discord.gg/Gz3dEH9VpJ</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

</main>

<footer>
  © 2026 XD Bot by <a href="https://discord.gg/Gz3dEH9VpJ" target="_blank">notcassal</a> &nbsp;·&nbsp;
  <span style="cursor:pointer;color:var(--muted)" onclick="switchTab('tos')">Terms of Service</span> &nbsp;·&nbsp;
  <span style="cursor:pointer;color:var(--muted)" onclick="switchTab('privacy')">Privacy Policy</span>
</footer>

<script>
  function switchTab(id) {
    document.querySelectorAll('.tab').forEach((t, i) => {
      t.classList.toggle('active', ['tos','privacy'][i] === id);
    });
    document.querySelectorAll('.page').forEach(p => {
      p.classList.toggle('active', p.id === id);
    });
    window.scrollTo({ top: 0, behavior: 'smooth' });
  }
</script>

</body>
</html>
